FBIS4-11094 "drlat078_a_94012" FBIS-LAT-94-078 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Delegate: Small-Island Teamwork Imperative Delegate: Small-Island Teamwork Imperative FL2104195994 Havana Radio Rebelde Network in Spanish 1700 GMT 21 Apr 94 FL2104195994 Havana Radio Rebelde Network Spanish BFN [Text] Pedro Luis Pedroso, a Foreign Ministry expert, believes that only cooperation among small island countries and decisive international support will make it possible for this group of nations to achieve sustainable development by the year 2,000. Pedroso pointed out Cuba's efforts in this regard, and ratified Cuba's willingness to help other nations. Pedroso is a member of the Cuban delegation to the First International Small Island Nations Sustainable Development Conference to be held from 25 April to 6 May in Barbados.
